description: This repository provides step-by-step code labs for popular machine learning frameworks: TensorFlow, PyTorch, scikit-learn, and Keras. Each guide covers installation, data preparation, model building, training, and deployment. Perfect for beginners and experts alike to enhance their ML skills and effectively utilize these powerful tools.
